I"w<h2 id="input-file-확장자-제한">input file 확장자 제한</h2>

<p>input의 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">accept</code>속성을 통해서 확장자 제한이 가능, 여러개의 확장자를 원할 경우 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">,</code>로 연결</p>

<p>자주 사용하는 확장자</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Excel Files(.xls)
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;input type="file" accept="application/vnd.ms-excel" /&gt;</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Excel Files (.xlsx)
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;input type="file" accept="application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet" /&gt;</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Text Files (.txt)
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;input type="file" accept="text/plain" /&gt;</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Image Files (.png/.jpg/etc)
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;input type="file" accept="image/*" /&gt;</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>HTML Files (.htm,.html)
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;input type="file" accept="text/html" /&gt;</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Video Files (.avi, .mpg, .mpeg, .mp4)
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;input type="file" accept="video/*" /&gt;</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Audio Files (.mp3, .wav, etc)
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;input type="file" accept="audio/*" /&gt;</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>PDF Files
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;input type="file" accept=".pdf" /&gt;</code></p>
  </li>
</ul>

:ET